Package: acr
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: AudioControl/Rust (ACR) application
 A Rust application for audio control functionality.
 This package provides tools for managing audio playback
 and control across different audio systems.
 .
 Includes command-line tools:
  * acr_dumpcache - Cache inspection utility
  * acr_lms_client - Logitech Media Server client
  * acr_send_update - Player state update utility
